item.title: Omfg someone please help with this compiler problem
item.dc:creator: @omg_dubzy omg dubzy
item.description:
@omg_dubzy wrote:

Eclipse has a clue in it’s name, to compile it, you need to download eclipse. Which for those who dont know is a java compiler/editor/runner. When you open your client with eclipse it automatically compiles it, as it’s part of the programs job to do so. I recommend downloading eclipse, unless you have a compiler already.

Need any more help skype me:
aquabutch

Thanks.
